[I] Converts text and other types of files to PostScript(TM)

[T] GNU enscript is a free replacement for Adobe's enscript program.
[T] enscript converts ASCII files to PostScript and spools the generated
[T] PostScript output to the specified printer or leaves it to file. Besides
[T] the standard ASCII to PostScript conversion, GNU enscript can do many
[T] other things.

[U] https://www.markkurossi.com/genscript/

[A] Markku Rossi <mtr@iki.fi>
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

